channel.title: Newest update look!
channel.description:
PLZ RATE IM NOT SURE IF THIS IS GOOD!!!
U rate it if u rate bad i will remove this from my server! rate from 0-10
I have a big dungeon(accely i have 3 but doesnt matter) now,i added abyssal for my slayer skill and just whit the abyss i added abyss leechers,walkers and guards
now i was thinking u need 85 slayer to attack an abyss but once u have that u can easely kill them and get whips so i made this.
once u have 85 slayer u can go in the dungeon cage (look picture below) also u need 85 slayer to attack abyssal demons just incase u get in there...
now i made this :
once u wanna attack a abyssal demon it will say u need to kill a abyssal leecher,guardian and walker first to attack an abyssal demon once u killd all 3 u can attack the abyssal demon once u killd it u need to kill another guard walker and leech to kill another abyss demon
i also made a abyssal book to tell u how to kill abyssal demons that will be dropped in the cage :)
good ?
PICTURE HERE : [img]http://img220.imageshack.us/img220/8923/examplewr5.png[/img]
prolly not working so [url=http://img220.imageshack.us/img220/8923/examplewr5.png]click here![/url]
NOTE THAT THE CAVE IS NOT DONE YET,need to add item drops and gfx so not done yet
